Stage 1: SPA / Browser Layer
+--------------------------+
|        User UI           |
|  (React / Next.js SPA)   |
|  - Deaf-first visuals    |
|  - State management      |
|  - HTTP requests         |
+-----------+--------------+
            |
            v
Stage 2: Flask Transistor Layer (Dev)
+--------------------------+
|   Flask App (sync)       |
|  - @app.route endpoints  |
|  - Parse request.json    |
|  - Parse request.args    |
|  - Parse request.form    |
|  - Return jsonify()      |
|  - Temporary adapter     |
+-----------+--------------+
            |
            v
Stage 3: AI Layer (Gemini / FastAPI)
+--------------------------+
|       Gemini AI          |
|  - NLP / GPT / AI logic  |
|  - GPU / TPU processing  |
|  - Structured JSON output|
|  - Optional async for high concurrency
+-----------+--------------+
            |
            v
Stage 4: Response / Rendering
+--------------------------+
|      SPA Receives        |
|  - JSON / AI output      |
|  - Updates UI visuals    |
|  - Optional templates    |
|  - Deaf-first presentation
+--------------------------+
